# Temporary/Untitled files (root-scoped only — leading slash anchors to repo root)
# Previously these were broad recursive patterns (`test-*.*`) which silently swallowed
# real test infrastructure files inside `apps/**/src/**` (e.g. test-fixtures.ts,
# test-helpers.ts, test-constants.ts) and caused CI test resolution failures while
# tests still passed locally. Scoping to root keeps the original intent (catching
# scratch/temp files dropped at the repo root) without burying tracked source code.
/Untitled-*.*
/untitled-*.*
/temp-*.*
/test-*.*

